---
title: Chermoula Beef Strips & Pea Pod Couscous Bowl with Greek Yoghurt & Roasted Almonds
description: Take your taste buds on a trip with this vibrant bowl of goodness. Juicy, chermoula-spiced beef strips brings bold, zesty vibes, perfectly paired with fluffy pea pod-speckled couscous. A dollop of creamy yoghurt adds a cool, tangy touch, while almonds bring the crunch. It’s fresh, flavourful, and oh-so-satisfying!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
